{"tid":797101,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"許文彪算唔算係陳錦鴻巔峰之作","createTime":"2018-08-28T08:59:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T12:54:41.000Z","uid":100804,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a10755d90e780992332604d490f85d1c9eb83a76","tid":797101,"uid":100804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T08:59:42.000Z","msg":"陳錦鴻歷來既最佳演出 <br />\n由佢最擅長既好人角色作為開頭 <br />\n跟住慢慢受到身邊既人同事所影響帶黎既性格演變 <br />\n佢演繹得可以話係入木三分,由其係佢比葉榮添迫佢收黑錢果幾幕...果種掙扎...非常精彩 <br />\n去到後黎放棄哂原來既做人原則,但奸得黎又令人對佢有所同情 <br />\n真係奸角中既異數 <img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20161002/photo/bkn-20161002212925393-1002_00862_001_01b.jpg?20161002215625\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20161002%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161002212925393-1002_00862_001_01b.jpg%3F20161002215625&h=9d9190d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OUXL9fuk-Rg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DOUXL9fuk-Rg&d=yWPJG85ZHa9pNZf8PcydowRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=c64d4d65\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OUXL9fuk-Rg</a>"},{"pid":"ac9a02e3802bf96332b8c2ab33a268d397549908","tid":797101,"uid":182930,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T09:24:53.000Z","msg":"我硬起呀，干將大哥"},{"pid":"55906236d63c67c5c6032032768c3337526fc84f","tid":797101,"uid":100804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T10:14:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e372630e821146b03fea82c28bd85184b8ab294","tid":797101,"uid":100804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T10:38:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19635be1a767edaf6b1c734d437298d53eb2d863","tid":797101,"uid":57570,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T10:58:34.000Z","msg":"本身許文彪葉榮添兩個角色寫得好<br />\n葉榮添幾奸都好，唔會搵朋友家人著數<br />\n許文彪家人關係差，又俾條女飛<br />\n一路只係靠自己原則企硬<br />\n偏偏葉榮添就要迫佢放棄原則<br />\n所以先一野墮落到谷底"},{"pid":"c84d3fccddc3fd08bdadd020118b5132f31747d5","tid":797101,"uid":100804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T11:56:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"384a02bd811c379c779aa9d92f0699a3948c429d","tid":797101,"uid":30176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T11:59:52.000Z","msg":"創世紀1 真係好撚好睇<br />\n50集高潮迭起<br />\n<br />\n許文彪由正變邪<br />\n羅嘉良 開頭型 後期假正義 做煩膠<br />\n郭晉安 典型戇鳩仔角色<br />\n<br />\n早兩年無線夜晚重播 <br />\n再睇番都重係完爆近十年電視劇"},{"pid":"0dd021183ccce8628466ade7400f83058dc973e1","tid":797101,"uid":9104,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T12:01:02.000Z","msg":"公平咩"},{"pid":"4acf40f982ab68392bc675f445142536e564434e","tid":797101,"uid":100804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"384a02bd811c379c779aa9d92f0699a3948c429d","tid":797101,"uid":30176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T11:59:52.000Z","msg":"創世紀1 真係好撚好睇<br />\n50集高潮迭起<br />\n<br />\n許文彪由正變邪<br />\n羅嘉良 開頭型 後期假正義 做煩膠<br />\n郭晉安 典型戇鳩仔角色<br />\n<br />\n早兩年無線夜晚重播 <br />\n再睇番都重係完爆近十年電視劇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T12:47:36.000Z","msg":"其實後50 集係唔係可以唔駛睇？又係tvb式三角戀"},{"pid":"ff0f90621f88023093fd281023280789219c4693","tid":797101,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T13:02:04.000Z","msg":"後期得巴不得爸爸楚帆係有印象，<br />\n嗰幅戇直正氣撚嘴臉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8a1f04e0aef9733074f4212d2ac82b2be293bff","tid":797101,"uid":113776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac9a02e3802bf96332b8c2ab33a268d397549908","tid":797101,"uid":182930,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T09:24:53.000Z","msg":"我硬起呀，干將大哥"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T13:03:56.000Z